lenders.name: Matt & Abby
lenders.loan_because:
Friends and Family! We're happy you have arrived at our Kiva site! Lack of access to sources of capital in developing regions is a huge impediment to growth. We have greatly benefited from the generosity of our families and those around us and would love to start a tradition of sustainable giving as we begin our lives together. That being said, we will both continue our lives as students for the foreseeable future and don't plan on making the big bucks for quite some time. The great thing about micro-finance, is that with careful management, your gift can be given over and over again as loans are reimbursed and redistributed. We would be absolutely honored if you would consider contributing to our Kiva fund for our wedding gift. These funds will be distributed in the form of micro-loans to entrepreneurs in developing countries per our discretion. Kiva partners with local micro finance organizations that work to screen potential borrowers. Historically, Kiva lenders have experienced a less than 1% default rate. As our loans are reimbursed, we plan to continue lending into the future. You can contribute to our account by pressing the "Send a Kiva Card" button below. 

Thank you for your support, Matt and Abby
